                Deo Aziz<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>ro <supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>alute <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ale</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">x</supplied>andri <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> et Iulia<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>u<supplied reason="lost">g</supplied>ustae Iulius <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>manus <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel wurde sekundär für eine Tür, dann für einen Grabbau wiederverwendet. (B): AE 1910, Mahler: Z. 1/2: Azi[zo p]/ro; Z. 2/3: [in]/vi[c]ti; Z. 3 (Ende): Iuli[ae]; Z. 4: Au[g]ustae.</p>
